      • menu

        public static int menu(java.util.Scanner kb)
        The menu method prompts the user for a menu choice.
        The menu choices are:
        1) Print the Store Inventory
        2) Sort the inventory by using the Natural Order
        3) Sort the inventory by the SKU using a comparator
        4) Sort the inventory by the Price using a comparator
        5) Quit
        The method ensures a value between 1 and 5 inclusive is entered.
        Parameters:
        kb - Representing a Scanner to the keyboard
        Returns:
        int - Representing the menu selection
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the Scanner object is null
